---
title: "_applyFeedInfoUpdates (Payment Abstraction V2 - PriceManager)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_check_empty: check adds.length and removes.length
    q_check_empty --> q_revert_empty: both empty
    q_revert_empty --> [*]: revert EmptyList()
    q_check_empty --> q_iter_removes: at least one non-empty

    q_iter_removes --> q_remove: for asset in removes
    q_remove --> q_hook_remove: _onFeedInfoUpdate(asset, true)
    q_hook_remove --> q_check_allowlisted: check s_allowlistedAssets.remove(asset)
    q_check_allowlisted --> q_revert_not_allowed: not in set
    q_revert_not_allowed --> [*]: revert AssetNotAllowlisted()
    q_check_allowlisted --> q_cleanup: removed from set
    q_cleanup --> q_iter_removes: delete feedId mapping, feedInfo, streamsPrice

    q_iter_removes --> q_iter_adds: removes complete
    q_iter_adds --> q_add: for feedInfo in adds
    q_add --> q_hook_add: _onFeedInfoUpdate(asset, false)
    q_hook_add --> q_validate_asset: check asset != address(0)
    q_validate_asset --> q_revert_zero: asset == address(0)
    q_revert_zero --> [*]: revert InvalidZeroAddress()

    q_validate_asset --> q_validate_feed: asset valid
    q_validate_feed --> q_revert_zero_val: stalenessThreshold == 0 AND both feedId and dataFeed zero
    q_revert_zero_val --> [*]: revert InvalidZeroValue()
    q_validate_feed --> q_check_streams: feed config valid

    q_check_streams --> q_validate_version: dataStreamsFeedId != 0
    q_check_streams --> q_store: dataStreamsFeedId == 0 (data feed only)

    q_validate_version --> q_revert_decimals: dataStreamsFeedDecimals == 0
    q_revert_decimals --> [*]: revert InvalidFeedDecimals()
    q_validate_version --> q_check_version: decimals valid
    q_check_version --> q_revert_version: version != 3
    q_revert_version --> [*]: revert InvalidFeedVersion()
    q_check_version --> q_check_rotation: version == 3

    q_check_rotation --> q_handle_rotation: previousAsset != address(0) AND previousAsset != asset
    q_check_rotation --> q_store: no rotation needed
    q_handle_rotation --> q_store: clean up previous asset streams state

    q_store --> q_iter_adds: s_feedInfo[asset] = feedInfo, update mappings

    q_iter_adds --> [*]: all adds processed

    note right of q_check_rotation
        INV-001: Feed ID rotation cleans up previous asset state
        INV-002: Previous asset must retain a data feed if its streams feed is rotated away
        INV-003: Only Data Streams report v3 is supported
        INV-004: _onFeedInfoUpdate hook allows BaseAuction to block changes during live auctions
    end note
